106
00:11:41.152 --> 00:11:42.318
Apa itu?

107
00:11:42.402 --> 00:11:44.443
"Tunjangan disabilitas"?

108
00:11:45.027 --> 00:11:47.151
Banyak sekali!

109
00:11:47.402 --> 00:11:49.735
Aku berjuang jiwa dan raga demi itu.

110
00:11:49.819 --> 00:11:51.235
Jangan bilang begitu.

111
00:11:56.694 --> 00:12:00.068
Mereka memilih tempat nostalgia.

112
00:12:00.151 --> 00:12:01.819
